{"tid":275140,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"各位單獨去旅行記得睇實自己的行李","createTime":"2017-06-07T21:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T11:00:28.000Z","uid":121401,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38a39fd88ae5277d1d7996b5306d38084a7688fd","tid":275140,"uid":121401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:06:55.000Z","msg":"尋日由日本返黎<br />\n<br />\n有個紮馬尾，約30歲，長黑衫，帶眼鏡的女人在機場行李輸送帶睇都唔睇個名牌就一手抽走我個gip,唔係喝住佢仲想拎走（唔駛2秒將件行李係輸送帶拎走）<br />\n<br />\n所以希望呢排返黎香港的大家，由其單獨，拎左行李先去廁所，仲有唔好擺貴重野落gip,盡量放袋。"},{"pid":"3720b02044579dea33d9f3e195408c8e1cfc3288","tid":275140,"uid":101557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:07:33.000Z","msg":"咁撚恐怖"},{"pid":"118b9033285f53d1f229f647a55420766060599b","tid":275140,"uid":121401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:09:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚恐怖</blockquote><br />\n係呀，我已經企到個行李口位好埋都比佢差d乘虛而入"},{"pid":"f467b7ef8b159331f8b43f12fcdb8d25431567ef","tid":275140,"uid":87182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實佢係搵食定係唔小心拎錯?"},{"pid":"f468021a70657e0d7d1bbf4b9e47e6e99782c12c","tid":275140,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:22:35.000Z","msg":"其實都好難防，去外國入境，你排 passport control 排得耐，入到 baggage claim 都隨時所有行李都到咗好耐。<br />\n<br />\n入沖縄試過成個鐘先入到境，去到 baggage claim ，連條帶都熄埋，啲行李喼都被搬到一角等人認領。"},{"pid":"cc37b44c804e4a3267d8ba0e6e1b5a62c339b637","tid":275140,"uid":54940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:28:50.000Z","msg":"其實諗落真係好唔安全<br />\n<br />\n就算上左鎖又點<br />\n<br />\n要整爆個喼總有方法<br />\n<br />\n賊人話拎就拎走"},{"pid":"717b14cbd20635b7d3443f5f270c38f0bc6bb515","tid":275140,"uid":36053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢係搵食定係唔小心拎錯?</blockquote><br />\n當佢拎錯<br />\n你啲嘢放晒入喼跟住無得用先係重點"},{"pid":"91187700dd80a2df238ca2deb89f772fe55cae66","tid":275140,"uid":2500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:41:36.000Z","msg":"去程擺得gip通常都係衫褲鞋襪<br />\n咁都好偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7a65efcdf0a8234ff0f76851f94e6d487a05b1","tid":275140,"uid":52116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:43:39.000Z","msg":"個喼咩牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee421d600ef6b61131fe22bb51dbe37f4a62497d","tid":275140,"uid":121401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去程擺得gip通常都係衫褲鞋襪<br />\n咁都好偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n回程，香港機場發生，所以叫大家小心"},{"pid":"6a7e48adca510f678a91f295c416bf4c376ab410","tid":275140,"uid":121401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個喼咩牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通牌子，1000樓下"},{"pid":"34e6609544aedfdd7d8674277c8923539ad46d2c","tid":275140,"uid":121401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都好難防，去外國入境，你排 passport control 排得耐，入到 baggage claim 都隨時所有行李都到咗好耐。<br />\n<br />\n入沖縄試過成個鐘先入到境，去到 baggage claim ，連條帶都熄埋，啲行李喼都被搬到一角等人認領。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以香港班地勤耐過西咁唔知好定唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab12cdde46ad04b6fb954e5523bfeccd7d51d142","tid":275140,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實都好難防，去外國入境，你排 passport control 排得耐，入到 baggage claim 都隨時所有行李都到咗好耐。<br />\n<br />\n入沖縄試過成個鐘先入到境，去到 baggage claim ，連條帶都熄埋，啲行李喼都被搬到一角等人認領。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以香港班地勤耐過西咁唔知好定唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n回程返香港直頭坐大機都揀機尾坐，反正落完機都仲要等行李<br />\n<br />\n去外國就咪制，3百幾人喺你前面，入境排到癲。"},{"pid":"d5764161f4bed907713b69ef975d03017647d7b1","tid":275140,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實都好難防，去外國入境，你排 passport control 排得耐，入到 baggage claim 都隨時所有行李都到咗好耐。<br />\n<br />\n入沖縄試過成個鐘先入到境，去到 baggage claim ，連條帶都熄埋，啲行李喼都被搬到一角等人認領。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以香港班地勤耐過西咁唔知好定唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔講佢係咪真心偷啦<br />\n但香港機場係好多盲毛<br />\n所以最好用D 唔常見既牌子同色<br />\n又者貼D 一睇就認到(人地一睇就知唔係自己既)既貼紙上去"},{"pid":"40b6b2477a2804609c4914ec6e36698e1ed3b529","tid":275140,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實都好難防，去外國入境，你排 passport control 排得耐，入到 baggage claim 都隨時所有行李都到咗好耐。<br />\n<br />\n入沖縄試過成個鐘先入到境，去到 baggage claim ，連條帶都熄埋，啲行李喼都被搬到一角等人認領。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以香港班地勤耐過西咁唔知好定唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔講佢係咪真心偷啦<br />\n但香港機場係好多盲毛<br />\n所以最好用D 唔常見既牌子同色<br />\n又者貼D 一睇就認到(人地一睇就知唔係自己既)既貼紙上去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買嘢加錢換果啲都成日見"},{"pid":"c22ed08fb195ff0d3a5cc864bff359ef771ffc00","tid":275140,"uid":71323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"加多啲奇奇怪怪個樣又突出嘅tag<br />\n個tag本身少見再加少人咁配搭<br />\n就防止人拎錯<br />\n<br />\n但防唔到老鼠"},{"pid":"0953b679495b71675f5589eb00e136730b35b190","tid":275140,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加多啲奇奇怪怪個樣又突出嘅tag<br />\n個tag本身少見再加少人咁配搭<br />\n就防止人拎錯<br />\n<br />\n但防唔到老鼠</blockquote><br />\n寫內有木雕"},{"pid":"453736e98804613dfcc149adf6637dc5daeb6090","tid":275140,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加多啲奇奇怪怪個樣又突出嘅tag<br />\n個tag本身少見再加少人咁配搭<br />\n就防止人拎錯<br />\n<br />\n但防唔到老鼠</blockquote><br />\n寫內有木雕</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi